There are 3main git project git sections which are:
  Git directory
  Working directory
  Staging area

There are 2 types of repository which are:
   Local repository
   Remote repository

Why Git:
   Open source
   Support data intergrity
   support roll-back
   Fast
   Collaboration is great

Source management platforms
   Github
   Gitlab
   Bitbucket (Stash)
   Amazone codecommit

In Git we have
   Git push: Push all changes from local repo to the remote repo
   Git pull: Brings all changes to the working area
   Git fetch: Brings specific changes to the local repo
   Git clone: brings the entire code to the working area

Branching
   Master ( or main) branch
   Development branch

